### Register User
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "user1",
  "lastName": "test",
  "email": "user1@mail.com",
  "password": "user1",
  "role": "USER",
  "profileImageUrl": "https://example.com/user.png"
}

